extends layout

block content

  if cert == 'OK'
    h1 Now you are our member! Log in and create Story now.
  else
    h1= title
    p Welcome to #[em Story Library], Good practice.

    p This is my new project start point!


    h1 Dynamic content  
  
    if error
      p Error getting dynamic content.
    else

      p The library has the following record counts:

      ul
        li #[strong Books:] !{data.book_count}
        li #[strong Stories:] !{data.story_count}
        li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}